    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone is balls! Flick your balls to victory in this billiards-like tactical RPG! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/fe2c7b6ed15e991b859bd4efbce981fc.avif?t=1770240765\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Angle your shots off of walls &amp; obstacles to find your path to success! Predictive trajectories help you make tricky shots if you can imagine them. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/381a638fa485014310d86fbe9e81d7e9.poster.avif?t=1770240765\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/381a638fa485014310d86fbe9e81d7e9.webm?t=1770240765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/381a638fa485014310d86fbe9e81d7e9.mp4?t=1770240765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect a cast of miniature characters! There are no micro-transactions, no FOMO - only the old fashioned grind. Every hero and monster can be recruited! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/cc447a0d97e144f77a1099fa694521f3.poster.avif?t=1770240765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/cc447a0d97e144f77a1099fa694521f3.webm?t=1770240765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310090/extras/cc447a0d97e144f77a1099fa694521f3.mp4?t=1770240765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize sets of skills to execute your strategies! Will you make a robust survivor, or a long range attacker?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated maps provide you with a new challenge each time you play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All characters are equally viable! There is no meta or tier list - the best one is the one you fancy most.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer mayhem! Will you work together, or get in each others' way?</p></li></ul>",
